name: Talisman Online
storyline: In the ancient orient, there is a peaceful and serene continent. The people there live and work in peace and contentment. Their families are kept there generation by generation. However, an evil power is preparing to come out behind the peaceful surface.
summary: Talisman Online is a free 3D fantasy MMORPG. with equipments, scenarios, various kinds of quests, and PVE & PVP stages.
